# PHYSICS::GET_ROPE_LAST_VERTEX_COORD

## Parameters
* **ROPE_INDEX** ropeID

## Returns
* **VECTOR**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Return the coordinates of last rope vertex. If rope wind/unwind last vertex may not be the last physical one.
